# Title: SyncAppvPublishingServer Execute Arbitrary PowerShell Code
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2021-07-12
# Level: medium
# Description: Executes arbitrary PowerShell code using SyncAppvPublishingServer.exe.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1218
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_lolbin_syncappvpublishingserver_execute_psh.yml
# False Positives:
#   - App-V clients

CommandLine="*\"n; *" Image="*\\SyncAppvPublishingServer.exe" OR OriginalFileName="syncappvpublishingserver.exe"